{
  "text": "We next establish additional monitoring-related properties of networks that let us further optimize the computation of the minimal beacon set. The concept of node arity in an undirected graph G(V, E), defined in [CITATION_1] , is useful for this discussion. Below, we restate the definition from [CITATION_2] in a slightly different manner.",
  "correct_citation": {
